verses.text: Unto \w the|strong="H4100"\w* \w end|strong="H5331"\w*, corrupt not, \w a|strong="H4100"\w* psalm \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w a|strong="H4100"\w* canticle \w for|strong="H0430"\w* \w Asaph|strong="H0623"\w*.

We \w will|strong="H2022"\w* praise thee, \w O|strong="H2142"\w* God: we \w will|strong="H2022"\w* praise, \w and|strong="H2022"\w* we \w will|strong="H2022"\w* \w call|strong="H2142"\w* upon thy name. We \w will|strong="H2022"\w* relate thy wondrous works:
When \w I|strong="H6471"\w* shall \w take|strong="H7311"\w* \w a|strong="H7311"\w* \w time|strong="H6471"\w*, \w I|strong="H6471"\w* \w will|strong="H3605"\w* judge justices.

\w The|strong="H7760"\w* earth \w is|strong="H7130"\w* melted, \w and|strong="H0226"\w* all \w that|strong="H7760"\w* dwell therein: \w I|strong="H7760"\w* have \w established|strong="H7760"\w* \w the|strong="H7760"\w* pillars thereof.

\w I|strong="H3045"\w* said \w to|strong="H0935"\w* \w the|strong="H0935"\w* wicked: \w Do|strong="H0935"\w* \w not|strong="H3045"\w* act wickedly: \w and|strong="H0935"\w* \w to|strong="H0935"\w* \w the|strong="H0935"\w* sinners: Lift \w not|strong="H3045"\w* \w up|strong="H0935"\w* \w the|strong="H0935"\w* horn.
Lift not up \w your|strong="H6258"\w* horn \w on|strong="H6258"\w* high: speak not iniquity against God.

\w For|strong="H0776"\w* neither \w from|strong="H0776"\w* \w the|strong="H7971"\w* east, nor \w from|strong="H0776"\w* \w the|strong="H7971"\w* west, nor \w from|strong="H0776"\w* \w the|strong="H7971"\w* desert hills:

\w For|strong="H0776"\w* \w God|strong="H0410"\w* \w is|strong="H0776"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* judge. \w One|strong="H3605"\w* \w he|strong="H0559"\w* putteth \w down|strong="H8313"\w*, \w and|strong="H0776"\w* another \w he|strong="H0559"\w* lifteth \w up|strong="H3605"\w*:

\w For|strong="H3045"\w* \w in|strong="H5750"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* hand \w of|strong="H5030"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* Lord \w there|strong="H0369"\w* \w is|strong="H0369"\w* \w a|strong="H7200"\w* cup \w of|strong="H5030"\w* strong wine full \w of|strong="H5030"\w* mixture. \w And|strong="H7200"\w* \w he|strong="H5704"\w* hath poured \w it|strong="H3045"\w* \w out|strong="H3045"\w* \w from|strong="H5704"\w* \w this|strong="H3045"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w that|strong="H3045"\w*: \w but|strong="H3808"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* dregs thereof \w are|strong="H4100"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* emptied: \w all|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* sinners \w of|strong="H5030"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* earth \w shall|strong="H3808"\w* drink.

But \w I|strong="H5704"\w* \w will|strong="H0430"\w* declare \w for|strong="H0430"\w* \w ever|strong="H5331"\w*: \w I|strong="H5704"\w* \w will|strong="H0430"\w* sing \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* \w God|strong="H0430"\w* \w of|strong="H0430"\w* Jacob.

\w And|strong="H3027"\w* \w I|strong="H4100"\w* \w will|strong="H3027"\w* \w break|strong="H7725"\w* \w all|strong="H3615"\w* \w the|strong="H7725"\w* horns \w of|strong="H3027"\w* sinners: \w but|strong="H3225"\w* \w the|strong="H7725"\w* horns \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w the|strong="H7725"\w* just \w shall|strong="H3027"\w* \w be|strong="H3027"\w* exalted.
